Title: Enemy Mine
Plot: When Earth's attempts to exploit a newly-discovered naquadah mine are thwarted by a tribe of indigenous Unas, SG-1 must turn to an old friend for help.
GuestStars: Michael Rooker, Steven Williams, Alex Zahara, Kavan Smith, G. Patrick Currie, Gary Jones, Michael Shore, Dean Redman, Kirk Caouette, Sean Tyson, Wycliff Hartwig
